Error 1, Try turning the orange head of the laser unit to make sure it is not blocked.
Error 2, Clean and tap the bumper slightly.
Error 3, Try moving the vaccum to a different place.
Error 4, Wipe the cliff sensors clean and move the vacuum to a different place.
Error 5, Remove and clean the main brush.
Error 6, Remove and clean the side brush.
Error 7, Make sure the wheels are not blocked, move the vacuum to a different place and try again.
Error 8, Make sure there are no obstacles around the vacuum.
Error 9, Install the dustbin and the filter.
Error 10, Make sure the filter has been dried or clean the filter.

Error 18, Suction fan malfunction. Please reboot the system.
Error 19, There is no current on the charging base. Check connection to a power supply.
Error 21, Please make sure that the top cover of the laser distance sensor is not pinned.
Error 22, Please wipe the dock sensor.
Error 23, Make sure the signal emission area of the dock is clean.
Error 24, No-Go-Zone or virtual wall detected. Please move the vacuum away from this area.
